{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"aria-valuemin 属性の使用","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuemin_attribute","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><code><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria/#aria-valuemin\" rel=\"external noopener\">aria-valuemin</a></code>&nbsp;属性は、スライダー、スピンボタン、プログレスバーなどの範囲ウィジェットに許容される最小値を定義するために使用されます。 <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuenow_attribute\">aria-valuenow</a></code> が既知の最大値と最小値を持つ場合、作成者は <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuemax_attribute\">aria-valuemax</a></code> と <code>aria-valuemin</code> のプロパティを提供する<strong>べき</strong>です（SHOULD）。 <code>aria-valuemin</code> の値は <code>aria-valuemax</code> の値以下で<strong>なければならない</strong>（MUST）。</span></p>\n\n<p><code>aria-valuemin</code>&nbsp;は、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/slider_role\">スライダー</a>、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_scrollbar_role\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">スクロールバー</a>、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_spinbutton_role\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">スピンボタン</a>のロールの<strong>必須</strong>属性です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>数値の文字列表現</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"possible_effects_on_user_agents_and_assistive_technology","title":"ユーザーエージェントと支援技術への影響","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>aria-valuemin</code> が <code>aria-valuemax</code> の値以下でない場合、これは支援技術によって処理されるエラー条件を生成します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>注</strong>: 支援技術がこの手法をどのように扱うべきかについての意見は異なる場合があります。 上記の情報は、これらの意見の1つで、したがって規範的ではありません。</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"example_1.3a\" name=\"Example_1.3A\">例 1:</h4>\n\n<p>下のスニペットは、最小値が 1 の単純なスライダーを示しています。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>slider<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-valuenow</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>4<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-valuemin</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-valuemax</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"used_with_aria_roles","title":"ARIA ロールで使用","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/progressbar_role\" title=\"Using_the_progressbar_role\">progressbar</a></li>\n <li>scrollbar</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/slider_role\" title=\"Using the slider role\">slider</a></li>\n <li>spinbutton</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"related_aria_techniques","title":"関連する ARIA 技術","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuemax_attribute\" title=\"Using_the_aria-valuemax_attribute\">aria-valuemax</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuenow_attribute\" title=\"Using the aria-valuenow attribute\">aria-valuenow</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuetext_attribute\" title=\"Using the aria-valuetext attribute\">aria-valuetext</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatibility","title":"互換性","isH3":true,"content":"<p class=\"comment\">TBD: 一般的な UA と AT 製品の組み合わせに関するサポート情報を追加する</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"additional_resources","title":"その他のリソース","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria/#aria-valuemin\" rel=\" noopener\">aria-valuemin の WAI-ARIA 仕様</a>（英語）</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"aria-valuemin 属性は、スライダー、スピンボタン、プログレスバーなどの範囲ウィジェットに許容される最小値を定義するために使用されます。 aria-valuenow が既知の最大値と最小値を持つ場合、作成者は aria-valuemax と aria-valuemin のプロパティを提供するべきです（SHOULD）。 aria-valuemin の値は aria-valuemax の値以下でなければならない（MUST）。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Utiliser l'attribut aria-valuemin","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/accessibility/aria/aria_techniques/using_the_aria-valuemin_attribute","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/accessibility/aria/aria_techniques/using_the_aria-valuemin_attribute/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility","title":"アクセシビリティ"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA","title":"ARIA"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques","title":"ARIA を使用する: ロール、ステート、プロパティ"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuemin_attribute","title":"aria-valuemin 属性の使用"}],"pageTitle":"aria-valuemin 属性の使用 - アクセシビリティ | MDN","noIndexing":false}}